  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the fenugreek leaves, shio cure, salt, and pepper, and stir well.",
    "Add the water to the pot and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with additional fenugreek leaves if desired."
